  "title": "Ace Your Cybersecurity Analyst Interview: A Beginner's Guide",
  "description": "This course provides a structured approach to mastering common cybersecurity analyst interview questions. Designed for beginners, it focuses on building a foundational understanding of key concepts and developing effective communication strategies to showcase your potential.",
